strings:
<voice_0x01001272><se_high>*: It's L-Leopold!
H-He's got David with the sceptre!

<voice_0x01001275><center>Now there are only two left...
<center>You will interfere no more...

<voice_0x01001277><se_def>David: H-He's... He's the only one who makes...
Master Dominico...happy...
<voice_0x0100127C><se_low>Dominico: David? Esteemed heir to the great sage Kupas?
<voice_0x0100127D><se_low>Dominico: ...Why has it taken me so long to realise?
<voice_0x0100127E><se_low>Dominico: I... I couldn't protect you... All the magic that has been in my family for generations...
<voice_0x0100127F><se_low>Dominico: My ancestors brought me and Kupas's heir together for a reason, but I...

<voice_0x01001280><se_low>Dominico: No! Just thinking about it is too painful!
It's unbearable!
